These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is golf is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | water | lemonade   |
| Sport      | volleyball    | golf  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: french, japanese, mexican
1. the french is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the japanese is on the far left##1
3. the japanese is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up     | milk      |
| Nationality   | japanese | french | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, apricot, tomato
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk  | coffee       |
| Food       | strawberry     | apricot | tomato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, potato, nectarine
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, sudoku, singing
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | nectarine    | potato     | raspberry |
| Hobby   | singing | fishing | sudoku     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, snake, fish
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, tram, car
1. the person driving the tram is the owner of the fish##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | snake | goat     | fish |
| Transport   | car        | boat | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, garlic, carrot
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, car
1. the person eating peas is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person eating carrot is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | carrot | peas      | garlic  |
| Transport   | scooter       | taxi | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, funk, indie
3 different pets are kept: goat, pony, hamster
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of funk is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | hip-hop     | funk    |
| Pet           | goat | hamster | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
