2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person eating pear is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | broccoli | lettuce | pear      |
| Hobby   | dancing     | fishing | magic-tricks |

