.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, hiking
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | hiking | traveling | drawing  |
| Pet     | guinea-pig     | chinchilla      | goldfish |

