.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, sports, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | hot-chocolate    | coffee    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | scientific | disaster |

