There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, indian, indonesian
1. the fan of funk is the pakistani##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the indonesian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | funk   | disco  |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | pakistani | indian |

