The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, nurse, freelancer
1. the nurse is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person eating lettuce is in the middle##1
3. the photographer is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | plum     | lettuce   | lime     |
| Job    | freelancer | nurse | photographer |

