1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the lawyer is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | architect    | lawyer | engineer |
| Pet   | horse | hamster     | rat        |

