.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, punk, techno
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | tea  | almond-milk | fanta  |
| Music-Genre   | punk | techno   | country |

