1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person eating artichoke is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | eggplant | apricot   | artichoke        |
| Sport   | baseball    | rowing | skateboarding |

