.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, apple, papaya
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, basketball, handball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | papaya | blueberry       | apple  |
| Sport   | handball  | basketball | parkour |

 